OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cof Lisa Dorrian
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof the murder of Lisa Dorrian.
OL,9,FThe 25-year-old from Bangor vanished
OL,10,Fon February 27, 2005 after attending a
OL,11,Fparty at Ballyhalbert Caravan Park.
OL,13,FDespite extensive searches in multiple
OL,14,Flocations and campaigning by her
OL,15,Ffamily, Ms Dorrian's body has never
OL,16,Fbeen found.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
