OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cof Lisa Dorrian
OL,6,FA 40-year-old woman was arrested in
OL,7,FBangor on Wednesday on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder, assisting offenders,
OL,9,Fwithholding information and preventing
OL,10,Fa lawful and decent burial.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Kerrie
OL,13,FForeman said: "The arrest comes just
OL,14,Fdays before the 21st anniversary of
OL,15,FLisa's disappearance and murder.
