OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772118239
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cof Lisa Dorrian
OL,6,F"Lisa was last seen alive on the night
OL,7,Fof Sunday 27 February 2005 in
OL,8,FBallyhalbert in County Down, and we
OL,9,Fbelieve she was murdered that night or
OL,10,Fin the early hours of the following
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,F"We remain determined to provide
OL,14,Fjustice for Lisa's family, and I would
OL,15,Fappeal to anyone with information
OL,16,Fabout her disappearance and murder to
OL,17,Fcontact detectives on 101."
